Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:00.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Numb your senses
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:03.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}No fairness is needed for pigs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:06.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Laughters above
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:09.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Playful smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Die get rolled
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:14.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Bathe in sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:18.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My tomorrow is built upon your flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Slay the last of your kind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:27.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}To reclaim what's rightfully mine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:23.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}Each time we'll enter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:25.06,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}First time to make this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:27.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs-1\pos(640,673)}Final dungeon 無念な未来の
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:29.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I have a reason
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:30.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't part the rivers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:33.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Surround them, off with their heads
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:34.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Christen my motive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}First time to notice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:38.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Final dungeon 群れて迷おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I hide among you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:40.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Facing my fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:44.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}At night I'm dreaming 永い夢の言葉
